input_args.text: "If you like the cutbacks to Social Security and other parts of the social safety-net that began during Bill Clinton's administration and escalated during Barack Obama's, then you will love Hillary Clinton. She is salivating like a hungry dog at the prospect of finishing off the remnants of FDR's New Deal that her husband started.\nYou can stop her and her co-conspirators in the Democratic and Republican parties. Vote for Jill Stein."
